, 4 Nov 1988, C. Dorworth (DAVFP 24977, dried culture PFC-053 only); Revelstoke, Jordan River, gravel pit S of the river, 
<geoCoordinate id="98CEA4693BDB055917AA645D283D8A51" degrees="48.4356" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="5" value="48.4356">48.4356N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="754381B91A365C26025B8CDF1A54E6AF" degrees="124.0140" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="5" value="-124.014">124.0140W</geoCoordinate>
, 24 Oct 1988, C. Dorworth (DAVFP 24978, dried culture PFC-055 only); ibid., 24 Oct 1988, T.N. Sieber (DAVFP 24979, dried culture PFC-067 only); Sooke, East Sooke Park, Babbington Trail, 
<geoCoordinate id="513145891786A3E257BCB1016CEA5896" degrees="48.3485" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="5" value="48.3485">48.3485N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="1F81E90830A65819E0F976669B85536A" degrees="123.6073" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="5" value="-123.6073">123.6073W</geoCoordinate>
